          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Spell-Like Abilities:</strong></span> At will-<span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch45.html#SpellsD-E21">detect good</a></em></span> and <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch45.html#SpellsD-E20">detect evil</a></em></span> within a 60-foot radius. Caster level 5th.</p>
